		<title>吴惠林：平议“修正资本主义”</title>
		<link>http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/6/19/n10495724.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 19 Jun 2018 03:08:57 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[专栏文集]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[评论]]></category>
