		<title>吴惠林：有感于本年诺贝尔经济学奖</title>
		<link>http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/17/11/21/n9871883.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 21 Nov 2017 02:32:33 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[专栏文集]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[评论]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[塞勒]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[衍生性金融]]></category>
